Turkey Brine

for 14-16lb bird 
1 c salt
1/2 c light brown sugar
1 gallon vegetable stock
1 tbsp black peppercorns
1/2 tbsp allspice berries
1/2 tbsp candied ginger
1 gallon iced water

Combine all ingredients except water into large stock pot and bring to a boil. Let cool to room temp, add ice water when ready to submerge bird.
